Schema Name Field Name Type Description <code>Mountaineers</code> <code>PublicEmail</code> String Public-facing email for mailing lists <p>This field is stored under the <code>customSchemas</code> object in each user's Google Workspace profile. Example JSON structure:</p> <pre><code>"customSchemas": {
  "Mountaineers": {
    "PublicEmail": "public-facing@example.com"
  }
}
</code></pre>
